Merafe Resources Says Third-Quarter European Ferrochrome Price Falls 11%

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-11T06:05:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/merafe-resources-says-third-quarter-european-ferrochrome-price-falls-11-.html
Merafe Resources Ltd. (MRF)  said the
third-quarter European benchmark ferrochrome price has been
settled at $1.20 per pound, an 11 percent decrease from the
second quarter.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  